              </div>
            </details>

            <details itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Question">
              <summary itemprop="name">What certifications should I look for in an e-waste recycler?</summary>
              <div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Answer" class="faq-answer">
                <p itemprop="text">Always verify KSPCB authorization. We hold KL/EW/628 — one of the few authorized facilities in Ernakulam district. We also provide NIST 800-88 data destruction and DPDP Act compliance documentation.</p>
              </div>
            </details>

            <details itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Question">
              <summary itemprop="name">Is EWaste Kochi certified and KSPCB authorized?</summary>
              <div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Answer" class="faq-answer">
